# custom
*sublime*
CLAUDE.md
.claude*

# --- Working / reference-only material (kept LOCAL, never committed) ---
# tmp/ holds local scratch work and the original reference material the tracked
# data/ store was derived from (see data/INVENTORY.md for provenance).
tmp/

# Raw California/CONUS GIS rasters parked for continuous soil/veg features and
# future domain extension (POLARIS/gNATSGO/LANDFIRE/LAI/3DEP/NLCD) — large,
# staged locally; only the small per-HRU derived CSVs are tracked. Provenance:
# data/raw_gis/SOURCES.md. The provenance doc + reusable HRU sampler are tracked.
data/raw_gis/*
!data/raw_gis/SOURCES.md
!data/raw_gis/sample_gis.py

# --- Derived data ---
# The forcing stores are tracked via git-LFS (see .gitattributes); any OTHER
# forcing/* file stays out of git. Small organized tables and the GeoPackage
# under data/ ARE tracked (see data/INVENTORY.md).
data/cdec15/forcing/*
!data/cdec15/forcing/historical_livneh_unsplit.nc
data/calsim/forcing/*
!data/calsim/forcing/historical_livneh_unsplit_9unimp.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/historical_livneh_unsplit_11obs.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/historical_livneh_unsplit_12rim.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/wgen_product_a_9unimp.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/wgen_product_a_11obs.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/wgen_product_a_12rim.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/historical_lto_9unimp.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/historical_lto_11obs.nc
!data/calsim/forcing/historical_lto_12rim.nc
outputs/

# Simulated outputs and diagnostic figures (derived); keep the folder + README.
artifacts/*
!artifacts/README.md
!artifacts/cdec15
!artifacts/calsim

# dPL: CANONICAL runs + the fidelity numerics gate + the track-record log are
# tracked (tiny nets — best.pt is ~60 KB); exploratory runs stay local under
# artifacts/dpl/testing/ (see artifacts/dpl/RUNS.md for the record + old->new map).
!artifacts/dpl
artifacts/dpl/*
!artifacts/dpl/RUNS.md
!artifacts/dpl/fidelity
!artifacts/dpl/hamon_dense
!artifacts/dpl/hamon
!artifacts/dpl/pt
!artifacts/dpl/noah
!artifacts/dpl/hybrid
!artifacts/dpl/hybrid_pet_dt
!artifacts/dpl/hybrid_progression.png
!artifacts/dpl/hybrid_progression.csv
!artifacts/dpl/dtdp_response_metrics.csv
!artifacts/dpl/figures
!artifacts/dpl/compare_val_kge.png

# Sphinx docs build output (generated by docs/ -> GitHub Pages)
docs/_build/
# regenerable dpl climatology/forcing sim cache (was under calsim/compare/)
artifacts/dpl/_climatology_cache/



